      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示用户通过SchedulerApp来管理事件和提醒的完整流程。核心是用Event和Reminder两个实体，分别对应EventDAO和ReminderService来处理持久化和调度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "Reminder",
        "ReminderService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我注意到Event和Reminder都关联了零售相关的模块，比如Retail_CouponSystem和Retail_Inventory。这是说事件类型绑定到优惠券系统，提醒绑定到库存模块吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Event",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
