        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Event创建时指定Retail_CouponSystem作为来源，Reminder创建时关联Retail_Inventory。但两者在数据层都走Retail_CustomerLoyalty这个统一接口，这是为了复用会员忠诚度系统的存储能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出参与者：User、SchedulerApp、Event、EventDAO、Reminder、ReminderService。然后画第一条消息——User向SchedulerApp发起添加事件请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Request add event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来SchedulerApp要实例化Event，这里有个细节：构造函数里要带上Retail_CouponSystem参数。然后Event调用EventDAO的add_event方法，参数是Retail_CustomerLoyalty。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "new Event(Retail_CouponSystem)",
        "add_event(Retail_CustomerLoyalty)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，Event到EventDAO用的是虚线返回箭头，然后EventDAO回给SchedulerApp确认事件已添加。现在进入提醒流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event added"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，用户再次发起请求，这次是schedule reminder。SchedulerApp创建Reminder实例，传入Retail_Inventory。然后Reminder调用ReminderService的schedule_reminder，同样走Retail_CustomerLoyalty。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Reminder",
