    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。Reminder到ReminderService是虚线调用，返回Reminder scheduled给SchedulerApp。最后还有查看事件的流程对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
